He'll belong to you

That you wish he'll be so alone without you

When you become in love
He'll be so with you forever
You can never hope for the seperation of the dove
Oh, you can only hope for his letter

The tears, if he doesn't, will be rain

Being lost to him is unthinkable
To see him differently is only something you can claim
Seeing him get hurt is unbearable

He thinks he knows you personally
But if he knew would he understand

I got blamed for flirtin with my friends boyfriend. Our friend Peter told me that she is blaming me for it. He said it was for a heads up. I talk to her the next day about it and she says no. Then a few days later, Peter tells me that he wasnt even supposed to tell me. So therefore she lied to me when i confronted her about it and she is blaming me for something i didnt do because i only see him once a week for about ten minutes and i barely talk to him then....so i really dont see how she could blame me for such a thing. I had this problem with someone else and its difficult because i always get blamed for this kind of stuff...I wouldnt do that to a friend. I am just not going to talk to her anymore if she is going to be like that
